(44, 15, 18, 49, 1, 4, 4, 'from the beginning of the world', 'Divine Knowledge and Choice', 'This connection highlights God''s foreknowledge of all his works and his choice of believers before the foundation of the world. Both passages emphasize God''s sovereignty and plan from the beginning.', 'theme', 0.37, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
